title: [Sharth's Weaponry]
description: Beneath an oak beam ceiling, a pair of wooden snowshoes hangs on one of the smooth white plaster walls.  A brass treasure chest sits in one corner while a suit of silver-chased armor rests on the gold oak floor.

A pair of wooden snowshoes hangs on one of the smooth white plaster walls, and an oak beam ceiling rises overhead.  A suit of silver-chased armor sits in one corner of a honey gold oak floor.  There is a lacquered wooden shelf on one side of the shop and a large brass-bound chest on the other.
